  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641090/extras/1db2183993769c38a624f260bd09c4b5.avif?t=1773069473\" width=548 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control of a blind old Hermit and his relentless study of an impending corruption.<br><br>Explore and solve block puzzles while being while threatened by intense hordes of vermin.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641090/extras/11ace5d5510778c9608b4f040b6ba590.poster.avif?t=1773069473\" width=1170 height=341 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641090/extras/11ace5d5510778c9608b4f040b6ba590.webm?t=1773069473\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find and collect abilities that can be used to destroy threats and break puzzles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Acquire abilities such as the Gun, the Hammer, Double Speed, Spin Attack, Stop Time, Health Extension, Block Bombs, the Shovel, and more</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Area specific puzzle mechanics tailored to each environment style. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open ended puzzles that can be solved in various ways. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect Abilities that alter the gameplay in various different ways.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect health upgrades to assist in resisting the hordes of vermin.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641090/extras/1db2183993769c38a624f260bd09c4b5.avif?t=1773069473\" width=548 height=160 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take control of a blind old Hermit and his relentless study of an impending corruption.<br><br>Explore and solve block puzzles while being while threatened by intense hordes of vermin.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641090/extras/11ace5d5510778c9608b4f040b6ba590.poster.avif?t=1773069473\" width=1170 height=341 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2641090/extras/11ace5d5510778c9608b4f040b6ba590.webm?t=1773069473\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find and collect abilities that can be used to destroy threats and break puzzles.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Acquire abilities such as the Gun, the Hammer, Double Speed, Spin Attack, Stop Time, Health Extension, Block Bombs, the Shovel, and more</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Area specific puzzle mechanics tailored to each environment style. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Open ended puzzles that can be solved in various ways. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect Abilities that alter the gameplay in various different ways.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect health upgrades to assist in resisting the hordes of vermin.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
